text: Skyhooks was an Australian rock band formed in Melbourne in March 1973 by Greg Macainsh on bass guitar and backing vocals, and Imants "Freddie" Strauks on drums. ==References== Category:1973 establishments in Australia Category:1980s disestablishments in Australia Category:1980 disestablishments Category:Australian rock bands Category:Musical groups established in 1973 Category:Musical groups disestablished in 1980 Category:Musical groups from Melbourne
